434
00:25:19,760 --> 00:25:22,260
<i>[Please let me get into the University of Tokyo, Kyohei Yuri]</i>

435
00:25:38,760 --> 00:25:41,790
It doesn't feel like New Year's anymore after the 3rd.

436
00:25:41,790 --> 00:25:44,420
We need to avoid crowds as much as possible.

437
00:25:44,420 --> 00:25:47,650
Plus, with fewer people here

438
00:25:47,650 --> 00:25:50,160
the gods can hear your wish better.

439
00:25:50,160 --> 00:25:52,380
Really?

440
00:25:52,380 --> 00:25:54,010
Maybe.

441
00:25:55,380 --> 00:26:00,290
But I'm sure the gods will have no trouble finding you.

442
00:26:00,290 --> 00:26:02,630
With your pretty pink hair.

443
00:26:03,710 --> 00:26:06,310
You really are a weird adult,

444
00:26:06,310 --> 00:26:08,100
Harumi.

445
00:26:13,260 --> 00:26:18,170
It was here when you first taught me.

446
00:26:19,470 --> 00:26:23,270
<i>It doesn't matter what your parents want.</i>

447
00:26:23,270 --> 00:26:25,400
<i>The knowledge that you obtain from studying</i>

448
00:26:25,400 --> 00:26:27,390
<i>is your own.</i>

449
00:26:28,220 --> 00:26:31,580
You've come a long way, Yuri-yuri.

450
00:26:31,580 --> 00:26:34,160
You almost got a finger cramp

451
00:26:34,160 --> 00:26:37,040
doing Fleming's rule back then, right?

452
00:26:39,830 --> 00:26:41,860
Thanks

453
00:26:43,180 --> 00:26:45,320
for everything, Harumi.

454
00:26:48,070 --> 00:26:51,010
You were the amazing one that wanted to study

455
00:26:51,010 --> 00:26:55,000
and decided to go to the University of Tokyo.

456
00:26:56,980 --> 00:26:59,670
When your father yelled at you,

457
00:26:59,670 --> 00:27:03,450
you could have just sulked and ran away.

458
00:27:05,620 --> 00:27:08,200
A person's choices

459
00:27:08,830 --> 00:27:11,480
can totally change their lives.

460
00:27:11,480 --> 00:27:14,800
<i>I love you. Marry me.</i>

461
00:27:23,980 --> 00:27:26,490
I chose you.

462
00:27:33,450 --> 00:27:35,040
I'm sorry.

463
00:27:36,970 --> 00:27:40,280
Let's return to cram school before we'll catch a cold.

464
00:27:44,130 --> 00:27:48,580
<i>I can't give him a false hope. </i>

465
00:27:50,320 --> 00:27:54,730
<i>His eyes won't easily be deceived.</i>

466
00:27:58,740 --> 00:28:01,360
