[Minami High School]</i>

468
00:28:03,250 --> 00:28:04,660
Yama-pyon!

469
00:28:04,660 --> 00:28:05,810
Morning!

470
00:28:05,810 --> 00:28:09,100
- Happy New Year!
- Keep coming to school if you want to graduate.

471
00:28:09,100 --> 00:28:10,460
- Sure!
- Okay!

472
00:28:10,460 --> 00:28:13,600
Except for you. Keep on studying.

473
00:28:14,320 --> 00:28:16,870
Did you go to the cram school during the New Year's holiday?

474
00:28:16,870 --> 00:28:18,520
Well...

475
00:28:18,520 --> 00:28:20,740
Harumi is surely amazing.

476
00:28:20,740 --> 00:28:24,460
She really turned you into a student preparing for the University of Tokyo.

477
00:28:24,460 --> 00:28:25,570
She's amazing.

478
00:28:25,570 --> 00:28:27,650
You're awesome yourself.

479
00:28:27,650 --> 00:28:31,580
How could you be with your beloved woman every day without pushing her down?

480
00:28:31,580 --> 00:28:36,330
I could only hold back... for three days? Not even that.

481
00:28:36,330 --> 00:28:38,810
I wouldn't be able to focus on studying because of my dirty thoughts.

482
00:28:38,810 --> 00:28:40,320
How can you call yourself a teacher?

483
00:28:40,320 --> 00:28:42,840
I'm glad that I'm switching jobs.

484
00:28:46,420 --> 00:28:50,890
I do look at her in a romantic sense.

485
00:28:50,890 --> 00:28:55,490
But I'm bearing with it. Just a little longer.

486
00:28:55,490 --> 00:28:59,160
Good. That's appropriate.

487
00:28:59,160 --> 00:29:03,300
You know, before...

488
00:29:03,300 --> 00:29:07,910
Don't worry. There was nothing going on between Harumi and me.

489
00:29:07,910 --> 00:29:10,730
We merely got drunk and slept the whole night.

490
00:29:13,550 --> 00:29:15,880
I just touched her slightly.

491
00:29:15,880 --> 00:29:18,910
I lied. Don't glare at me like that!

492
00:29:18,910 --> 00:29:22,850
Now you can take the exam without any worries.

493
00:29:22,850 --> 00:29:24,290
Yes.

494
00:29:31,440 --> 00:29:34,070
<i>[7 days until the National Center Test for University Admissions]</i>

495
00:29:35,600 --> 00:29:39,770
Hereby my lessons before the Center Test come to an end.

496
00:29:39,770 --> 00:29:43,760
Please don't forget to review thoroughly until the test.

497
00:29:45,030 --> 00:29:48,170
There's a lot I want to say to you, but...

498
00:29:48,170 --> 00:29:50,900
I pray for you from the bottom of my heart.

499
00:29:50,900 --> 00:29:54,250
I hope you'll see familiar questions on your tests,

500
00:29:54,250 --> 00:29:58,280
and for you two to pass the exam.

501
00:30:01,120 --> 00:30:05,190
- Sensei-
- I'll accept your gratitude once you passed.

502
00:30:05,190 --> 00:30:08,130
Here is my number.

503
00:30:08,130 --> 00:30:11,890
One month after you pass the test,

504
00:30:11,890 --> 00:30:14,580
there will be a second test to take.

505
00:30:14,580 --> 00:30:16,680
That's the real test.

506
00:30:16,680 --> 00:30:20,300
Until then, please contact me anytime if you have any questions.

507
00:30:20,300 --> 00:30:22,330
It's a special offer only for you guys.

508
00:30:34,090 --> 00:30:36,170
Thank you for everything.

509
00:31:03,330 --> 00:31:06,300
<i>[Preparing for Business]</i>

510
00:31:06,300 --> 00:31:07,740
All right,

511
00:31:07,740 --> 00:31:10,840
my lesson's over now.

512
00:31:11,440 --> 00:31:14,790
Since you guys were able to focus with that delicious smell,

513
00:31:14,790 --> 00:31:17,460
you can handle anything during the exam.

514
00:31:17,460 --> 00:31:20,020
Here you go. It's on the house.

515
00:31:20,020 --> 00:31:21,950
Thank you.

516
00:31:21,950 --> 00:31:24,070
Thank you for letting us use your place.

517
00:31:24,070 --> 00:31:26,920
If you'd like, you can stay here a little longer.

518
00:31:26,920 --> 00:31:28,010
I'll go to the restroom.

519
00:31:28,010 --> 00:31:31,160
Of course!

520
00:31:31,160 --> 00:31:35,320
Say, who was the person who broke your heart?

521
00:31:35,320 --> 00:31:40,770
It's Junko. I gave her freebies and discounts.

522
00:31:40,770 --> 00:31:45,430
I even made heart-shaped mayonnaise, but she didn't notice me at all.

523
00:31:45,430 --> 00:31:49,740
You can't get through to a study zombie this way.

524
00:31:49,740 --> 00:31:51,470
You know...

525
00:31:51,470 --> 00:31:56,210
I'm upset, but I'll give up since she's marrying Masashi.

526
